column2: SELECT a.z, a.logMass, a.t_age_mean, a.metallicity_mean, a.dust1_mean, a.tau_mean, a.age_mean, a.ssfr_mean, d.w1flux, d.w1sigflux, d.w2flux, d.w2sigflux, d.w3flux, d.w3sigflux, d.w4flux, d.w4sigflux, p.modelFlux_u, p.modelfluxIvar_u, p.modelFlux_g, p.modelFluxIvar_g, p.modelFlux_r, p.modelFluxIvar_r, p.modelFlux_i, p.modelFluxIvar_i, p.modelFlux_z, p.modelFluxIvar_z from stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as a INNER JOIN SpecPhotoAll as b on a.specObjID = b.specObjID LEFT JOIN WISE_xmatch as c on b.ObjID = c.sdss_objid LEFT JOIN WISE_allsky as d on c.wise_cntr = d.cntr LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on b.objID = p.objID ORDER BY b.objID ASC
